_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, The Queen's Hand.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Epilogue_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Epilogue (A Dance with Dragons)\">Epilogue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123449\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.084 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.262 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1420/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10879/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7475/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 881/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4022/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.68 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  250.953      1 -total\n 76.57%  192.148      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 75.68%  189.916      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.77%   32.047      1 Template:For\n 10.15%   25.463     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  8.74%   21.926     11 Template:Ref\n  5.84%   14.652     11 Template:Ref/core\n  3.15%    7.899      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.75%    4.395      2 Template:Quote\n  1.10%    2.766      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:13396-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403123449 and revision id 311646\n -->\n",
